init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: A code that needs to be activated only in cases of the utmost urgency.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Scared and confused at the same time, you ask "What has happened?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He hands me a folder with the words "You're our last hope" on the cover.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I turn the dial all the way to the right and all of the people from that reality disappear.
